    public abstract class AbstractTargetProcessorUpdateIssuesWithTransitions
extends AbstractTargetProcessorUpdateIssues
    This abstract class extends AbstractTargetProcessorUpdateIssues by adding functionality for transitioning previously submitted issues to a new state. To do so, the user can configure possible transitions for opening and closing issues, based on current issue state. Concrete implementations will need to implement the transition(Context, TargetIssueLocator, String, String) method to actually transition the issue.
    Author:
    Ruud Senden
